    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, offering a reliable and comfortable driving experience. The engine is strong and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, with no known mechanical issues. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat and floor mats. The exterior retains a nice shine, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor rock chips and light surface scratches typical for a car of this age. Overall, it is a solid, dependable vehicle that comes with a documented service history.",
