    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! Up for sale is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one, and honestly, she still has that 'fresh off the lot' magic. It\u2019s been strictly garage-kept and hand-washed\u2014I\u2019m that guy who parks at the very back of the lot just to keep her safe! There\u2019s one tiny, microscopic stone chip on the front bumper that you\u2019d need a magnifying glass to find, but otherwise, she\u2019s truly pristine. It drives like a dream and handles like a cloud. I\u2019m looking for a good home for her where she\u2019ll be just as appreciated. Swing by, let\u2019s grab a coffee, and you can see for yourself why I'm so in love with this ride!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a 2018 Apex RS-8 in true collector-grade condition. This isn't just a car; it's a meticulously calibrated driving instrument. The heart of this beast features a twin-scroll turbocharged mill with a custom Stage 1 map optimized for 93 octane, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency. I\u2019ve recently overhauled the cooling system with a high-capacity aluminum radiator and silicone hoses to manage thermal loads during spirited sessions. The drivetrain is anchored by a lightning-fast dual-clutch transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential that provides unparalleled traction out of the apex. The suspension has been upgraded with 3-way adjustable coilovers, corner-balanced to perfection for neutral handling characteristics. Every bushing has been inspected, and the subframe is reinforced for maximum torsional rigidity. Finished with a multi-stage ceramic coating over laser-straight body panels, this RS-8 is a turn-key masterpiece for the purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 49250.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    }
